						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken hero-stone in the temple of Vīrabhadra.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription commemorates the death of <hi rend="bold">Sōva-gauvuḍa,</hi> who died in a cattleraid at <hi rend="bold">Bēḍage</hi> (modern Byāḍgi). The characters are of about the <hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

